Anglo American May Sell Stake in Iron Ore Mine, Independent Says

-- B y   I s i s   A l m e i d a
-- 
2011-06-05T11:23:00Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-05/anglo-american-may-sell-stake-in-iron-ore-mine-independent-says.html
Anglo American Plc (AAL)  may sell a stake
in an iron ore mine in  Brazil , the Independent on Sunday
reported, without saying where it got the information.  The company discussed having a partner in the Minas-Rio
project on many occasions over the past few years, the newspaper
said, citing an unidentified spokeswoman. Anglo American
continues to explore a range of options for the project,
according to the newspaper.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Isis Almeida in London at 
 Ialmeida3@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Dick Schumacher at 
 dschumacher@bloomberg.net . 